{"title":"西陵峡口——三峡组诗之一","authors":["方纪"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":8,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西陵峡口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——三峡组诗之一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陡峭的山峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然遮蔽了黎明的青光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江水暗淡了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船头激起黑色的波浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄牛——那矗立江心的巨石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一个庞大的怪物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎面扑来……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船只又灵巧地闪在一旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船只像驶进了深渊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峡风呼哨，江水沸腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨星来不及隐去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被悬挂在那黑色的峭壁上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空复盖在头上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一个昏暗的池塘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只在那高与天齐的峰顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又闪现了黎明的青光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船长走进驾驶台来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望望天空说：天要亮了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果然，转过迎面的山峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曙光照进驾驶台上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江水横流，激起银花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨雾从江面散去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山峰揭去了头纱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳照进了西陵峡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳照在红旗上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗飘飘像朝霞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趸船矗立大江心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻机高耸像宝塔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽笛响了，汽笛问道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——你在这里做什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻机响了，钻机回答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我要开发西陵峡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里将筑起拦江大坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑起那使船只爬山的船闸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成排的涡轮机埋伏在地下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愤怒的江水会发出火花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江将服从人的支配，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水被拦蓄在三峡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山会变成大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市将建筑在神女峰下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，这里是钻机在开路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水文队在测量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航测机在飞行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科学家们在思索。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天，这里会变成工地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始那世界上最伟大的工程；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了征服长江，成千上万的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢的人将来到三峡！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}